{"id":43937,"title":"MRI with spin labeling for diagnosis of early chronic pancreatitis.","abstract":"The purpose of this article is to discuss MRI with spin labeling for diagnosis of chronic pancreatitis.Because of the unique functional information it can provide, MRI with spin labeling appears to be a useful adjunctive technique that can be added to routine anatomic imaging of the pancreas and pancreatic duct.","date":"2014-04-24","categories":"Digestive System Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24758656","annotations":[{"name":"Magnetic resonance imaging","weight":0.814657,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Magnetic_resonance_imaging"},{"name":"Pancreas","weight":0.795537,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pancreas"},{"name":"Anatomy","weight":0.786341,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anatomy"},{"name":"Medical imaging","weight":0.710232,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medical_imaging"},{"name":"Diagnosis","weight":0.657965,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diagnosis"},{"name":"Pancreatitis","weight":0.409801,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pancreatitis"},{"name":"Pancreatic duct","weight":0.292341,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pancreatic_duct"},{"name":"Chronic pancreatitis","weight":0.162801,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chronic_pancreatitis"},{"name":"Chronic (medicine)","weight":0.0551856,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chronic_(medicine)"},{"name":"Adjunct (grammar)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adjunct_(grammar)"},{"name":"Isotopic labeling","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Isotopic_labeling"},{"name":"Information","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Information"},{"name":"Spin (physics)","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spin_(p